data.event: Barb Modrack bmodrack@gannett.com March 23, 2009 From LSJ.com She was pulled from the bank of an island by a bystander, and airlifted to Sparrow Hospital, but did not appear to suffer life threatening injuries, said Grand Ledge Police Chief Martin Underhill.
